        {
            "id": "block_3f15ff5b45b62a6f88bc0de39e399b5d",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "reverse", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Real-World Ready",
            "heading": "Built for Real-World Projects",
            "body_html": "<p>Bryntum Gantt is built to tame real-world complexity and streamline project planning via smart, intuitive tools:</p> <ul class=\"two-columns\"> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Track the pace of progress with an </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/s-curve/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S-curve</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Compare task durations across </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/planned-percent-done/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">baselines and chart completion percentages</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Surface </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/criticalpaths/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">critical path</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">s to speed up project delivery.</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/conflicts/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Settle</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> or </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/postponed-conflicts/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">defer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> scheduling conflicts to keep your plan intact.</span></li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "Bryntum Gantt is built to tame real-world complexity and streamline project planning via smart, intuitive tools: Track the pace of progress with an S-curve . Compare task durations across baselines and chart completion percentages . Surface critical path s to speed up project delivery. Settle or defer scheduling conflicts to keep your plan intact.",
            "links": [
                {
                    "text": "S-curve",
                    "href": "https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/s-curve/"
                },
