        {
            "id": "block_2c3c61d9aa0568d9d622dade60699342",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Performance",
            "heading": "Lightning-Quick",
            "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Written in modern JavaScript (ES6+) for swift, efficient execution, Bryntum Gantt is tuned for speed so teams stay focused on planning:</span></p> <ul> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Comfortably handle </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/bigdataset/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">huge datasets</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and advanced features.</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Keep interactions fluid and responsive with instant updates.</span></li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "Written in modern JavaScript (ES6+) for swift, efficient execution, Bryntum Gantt is tuned for speed so teams stay focused on planning: Comfortably handle huge datasets and advanced features. Keep interactions fluid and responsive with instant updates.",
