            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Component Library",
            "heading": "50+ Additional Widgets",
            "body_html": "<p class=\"p1\">Pick from a <a href=\"/products/gantt/examples/kitchen-sink/\">broad set of UI elements</a> that quickly give your app a polished, professional feel:</p> <ul class=\"ul1\"> <li class=\"li1\">Drop in <strong>chat boxes, menus, toggles, sliders and more</strong> alongside your Bryntum Gantt chart.</li> <li class=\"li1\">Cut clicks and searching to meet user needs faster.</li> <li class=\"li1\">Wire up widgets straightforwardly via our clear docs.</li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "Pick from a broad set of UI elements that quickly give your app a polished, professional feel: Drop in chat boxes, menus, toggles, sliders and more alongside your Bryntum Gantt chart. Cut clicks and searching to meet user needs faster. Wire up widgets straightforwardly via our clear docs.",
