        {
            "id": "block_308bfebd6b6058ced7d49c6b5f4ae83d",
            "type": "text-mini-demo",
            "eyebrow": "Try It Yourself",
            "heading": "The Most Flexible JS Gantt on the Web",
            "body_html": "<p class=\"pre-title\">From developers, to developers</p>  <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Gantt chart wraps up a huge amount of complexity. We give you a clean, deeply configurable and thoroughly tested API, so the small details aren’t your problem.</span></p>",
            "body_text": "From developers, to developers  A Gantt chart wraps up a huge amount of complexity. We give you a clean, deeply configurable and thoroughly tested API, so the small details aren’t your problem.",
