            "demo_kind": "gantt",
            "demo_position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "block_9acd2c85d89f9b4d895ff10ee9aac96e",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["video-file", "reverse", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Scheduling Engine",
            "heading": "Top-Tier Scheduling Engine",
            "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The JavaScript Gantt engine briskly handles asynchronous scheduling across any number of tasks, taking dependencies, constraints and scheduling modes into account.</span></p> <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Designed independently of the DOM, it can also run server-side on Node.js.</span></p> <h6 style=\"margin-top: 1em;\">Animated Redraws</h6> <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Moving a task kicks off a smooth animation that reveals how dependent tasks shift in response.</span></p>",
            "body_text": "The JavaScript Gantt engine briskly handles asynchronous scheduling across any number of tasks, taking dependencies, constraints and scheduling modes into account. Designed independently of the DOM, it can also run server-side on Node.js. Animated Redraws Moving a task kicks off a smooth animation that reveals how dependent tasks shift in response.",
            "links": [],
            "ctas": [],
            "media": [
                {
                    "kind": "video",
                    "src": "../assets/gantt/animated-redraw-big-dataset-3.mp4",
                    "src_original": "https://bryntum.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/animated-redraw-big-dataset-3.mp4"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "block_492ed05bbe9a04fbfdaa3f90f6a12ed8",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["video-file", "white-section", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Task Editing",
            "heading": "Tailorable Task Editor and Menu",
            "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The built-in </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/taskeditor/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">task editor</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is designed to be extended and shaped freely in the JS Gantt chart. Make it fit your workflow exactly:</span></p> <ul> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Adjust which fields are visible</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bring your own custom tabs</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/taskmenu/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tweak</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> or </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/custom-taskmenu/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">swap out</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> the right-click task menu.</span></li> <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tailor the </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/resourceassignment/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">resource picker</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "The built-in task editor is designed to be extended and shaped freely in the JS Gantt chart. Make it fit your workflow exactly: Adjust which fields are visible Bring your own custom tabs Tweak or swap out the right-click task menu. Tailor the resource picker .",
            "links": [
