        {
            "id": "block_ff5073f8911439ab5fdb152e35e4e182",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "reverse", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Integrations",
            "heading": "Integrations and Export Options",
            "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The JavaScript Gantt chart plays nicely with other tools and ships with a versatile set of export options to keep your team and stakeholders in the loop.</span></p> <ul> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Drop in a </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/joint-js/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">PERT chart</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></li> <li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Push Gantt data to </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/exporttoexcel/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Microsoft Excel</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> or to </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/msprojectexport/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Microsoft Project</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/print/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">print it</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, or share it as </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/export/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">PDF, PNG</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/export-to-ics/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ICS</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></li> <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pair Gantt with other Bryntum components such as </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/gantt-schedulerpro/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Scheduler Pro</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/gantt/examples/gantt-taskboard/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Task Board</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "The JavaScript Gantt chart plays nicely with other tools and ships with a versatile set of export options to keep your team and stakeholders in the loop. Drop in a PERT chart . Push Gantt data to Microsoft Excel or to Microsoft Project , print it , or share it as PDF, PNG and ICS . Pair Gantt with other Bryntum components such as Scheduler Pro and Task Board .",
